Package: breaks
Title: Interactive Watershed Break Point Delineation
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-03-10
Authors@R: c(
    person("Al", "Irvine", email = "al@newgraphenvironment.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("New Graph Environment Ltd.", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Interactive Shiny app for clicking stream networks to place break
    points, delineating upstream watersheds, and exporting sub-basins via
    pairwise subtraction. Built on the fresh package for FWA-referenced
    spatial hydrology queries.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/NewGraphEnvironment/breaks,
    https://www.newgraphenvironment.com/breaks/
